"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/78760","Home Office","false","2014-07-22","<p> </p><p>The cost of the re-instatement of Campsfield House was met fully by the <br>operator, MITIE, and their insurers.</p><p> </p>","Staffordshire Moorlands","Karen Bradley",,"2014-07-22T10:21:59.9189544Z","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/78760/answer","Biography information for Karen Bradley","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/78760/answer",,,,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/78760/answer",,,,,"1","Home Office","Home Office","2014-07-17","Campsfield House Immigration Removal Centre","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for the Home Department, who met the costs of damaged caused by the fire in October 2013 at Campsfield House, Oxfordshire.","false","Biography information for Mr Andrew Smith","Oxford East","Mr Andrew Smith","206467"
